    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.84) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.53)) * wp.sin(0.56))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.12) + (tmp + 0.94 + v0 + 0.12)) - wp.exp(0.84))
    v1 = 0.05
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(tmp + 0.13) * (v2 + 0.26 + v0 + 0.69)))
    v1 = 0.71
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v0 + 0.85 * v0 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
